{"type": "article", "id": 2804, "title": "多功能杂志桌", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-13T08:22:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232611SlDcHC9zrfXeO56w.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自澳大利亚墨尔本的设计师 Brad Wray 日前带来一款多功能杂志桌，整个桌子的框架用水泥做成，平面桌板则选用了木头材质，两种材料形成强烈的对比。这是一款可灵活操作的作品，用户既可以把木板放置在水泥框架上当作桌面、或者坐凳，也可以把它收起来。在摆放方式上，既可以作为咖啡桌与边桌，也可以作为杂志收纳架或坐凳，完全可以根据自己的实际需求来做。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232608MtqSYaT37rBN8eAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232609T308yoPfs64JAWqx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232609YXBmbsEe07WzQd6K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232610zXk7YxojTHGRrL0Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}